Package com.jswiff

Class Summary
MediaImporter Helper class for media import.
SWFDocument This class represents a Macromedia Flash (SWF) document.
SWFReader This class reads an SWF file from a stream, invoking registered listeners to process the SWF.
SWFWriter This class writes an SWF document (an SWFDocument instance) to an output stream.
